PersonalMission.Name: LT-13: The Key to Victory
PersonalMission.Description: Victory is easier to achieve when you are part of a Platoon, and even more so when your tactical unit is well coordinated. While you are distracting the enemy and relaying their position, your Platoon members will cause damage to targets spotted by you, bringing your team one step closer to victory. This mission may be completed either as part of a Platoon or on your own; however, the latter is much more difficult.
PersonalMission.Hint: If you join a battle as part of a Platoon, make sure that you have solid voice communication among your Platoon members. This will help to save the time you usually spend typing messages in Chat.

Primary.Conditions:
•  Enable your allies to cause 2,500 HP of damage
•  Cause 2,000 HP of damage (personal/Platoon)
